caption.title: Lake surface temperature model parameters and fit.
caption.p: Summary of lake temperature data (period of record) used to parameterize models of surface temperature and the parameter values for lake surface temperature models* (sensu [ 38]). The Nash-Sutcliff Coefficient (NSC; 1 = perfect fit) is a measure of model fit for non-linear logistic regression models [ 38].
